# G5 — every mission and its operation, drawn as a graph.
# Operations cluster in the layout: INHERENT RESOLVE will be the largest
# hub (10 missions), with smaller operations scattered. This is the same
# data as the tabular q4_missions_by_cocom but rendered as a graph so you
# can see the relative density at a glance.
#
# Click any operation node to see all the missions that link to it.

match
  $m isa mission;
  $m links (operation: $op, mission-document: $doc);
